cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.SE 

The paper discusses techniques for protecting the intellectual property of deep neural networks, which is a security and privacy concern (cs.CR). The techniques involve modifying the model architecture and/or weights, which is related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also evaluates the performance of the techniques using various metrics, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and software engineering (cs.SE).
